new man do come shall give you my opinin, whilst yett lotter is the best

beeter, for our siddy & all our endeavour must be to have all advantages that can
te exspected from the northren trade, & in case wee do finde this new man the best
I am contented to allow 4 to you to seenne the goods from hn att Hull
